"Supported Formats: PDF, PS, Tiff, DjVu, Images, DVI, XPS, Fiction Book, "
"Comic Book, Plucker, EPub, Fax"
msgstr ""
"Formats acceptats: PDF, PS, Tiff, DjVu, imatges, DVI, XPS, Fiction Book, "
"llibres de còmic, Plucker, EPub, Fax"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
